			<div class="themedArea">
			<h1 id="node-js-really-">Node.js (really)</h1>
<ul>
<li><p>V8</p>
<ul>
<li>JavaScript engine</li>
<li>Used in Chrome/Chromium (and node.js)</li>
<li>Event Loop</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li><p>Node.js core APIs</p>
<ul>
<li>REPL</li>
<li>Module system/module loader</li>
<li>fs (filesystem), os (operating system), buffer (memory)</li>
<li>net (TCP), http (http), dns (DNS)</li>
<li>child_process, cluster</li>
<li>util, url, path</li>
<li>and some others, total modules only ~ 25 </li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>

			</div>
			
			</div>
		
		</div>
	
		
