			<div class="themedArea">
			<h1 id="conventions">Conventions</h1>
<ul>
<li>Asynchronosity<ul>
<li>Callbacks</li>
<li>Error first convention</li>
<li>Callback hell</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>package.json<ul>
<li>God file for a Node project</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>Modularity<ul>
<li>Teeny tiny modules doing one thing only</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>Using build tools and task runners<ul>
<li>Static checking</li>
<li>Hot reloading</li>
<li>Over engineering</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>Tiny core, everything else in userland</li>
</ul>

			</div>
			
			</div>
		
