			<h1 id="npm">NPM</h1>
<ul>
<li>NPM - Node Package Manager (think Maven)</li>
<li>Bundled into node</li>
<li>Dependency management</li>
<li>Build tool/Script runner</li>
<li>Very Github centric</li>
<li>Extremely easy to build and publish modules</li>
<li>node_modules</li>
<li>Tiny modules by convention</li>
<li>Contains modules for:<ul>
<li>Node.js</li>
<li>Mobile</li>
<li>Browsers</li>
<li>IoT</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>

