			<div class="themedArea">
			<h1 id="usage-yes">Usage - Yes</h1>
<ul>
<li>Real time applications</li>
<li>Building APIs<ul>
<li>Especially ones connecting to multiple different places </li>
<li>Or ones using object database</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>Applications needing fast response</li>
<li>Queued inputs<ul>
<li>In front of RabbitMQ,    ZeroMQ etc.</li>
<li>Places where "eventual consistency" is enough</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>Data Streaming<ul>
<li>Processing content while it's still coming in</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>Proxying</li>
<li>Frontend tooling</li>
<li>Isomorphic JS Applications - The holy grail</li>
</ul>

